---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Corporate Social Responsibility - Green Orbit Digital">
  <Header />
  <main class="py-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="Corporate Social Responsibility" 
      highlightText="CSR"
      description="Driving positive social and environmental impact while delivering sustainable business value."
    />

    <section title="What is CSR?">
      <p>
        Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) is the commitment of businesses to act ethically, 
        contribute to economic development, and improve the quality of life of employees, 
        communities, and society at large.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section title="Key CSR Areas">
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Social Impact:</strong> Employee welfare, community engagement, education, and equality.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Stewardship:</strong> Sustainable operations, carbon reduction, resource management, and green innovation.</li>
        <li><strong>Economic Responsibility:</strong> Transparent governance, ethical business practices, and long-term value creation.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Why CSR Matters">
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Strengthens brand reputation and stakeholder trust.</li>
        <li>Enhances employee engagement and retention.</li>
        <li>Supports sustainable growth and alignment with global goals, such as the UN SDGs.</li>
        <li>Encourages responsible business practices across the value chain.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Our CSR Approach">
      <p>At Green Orbit Digital, we integrate CSR principles across our operations and client services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Community Programs – Education, mentoring, and outreach initiatives in the space and digital sectors.</li>
        <li>Environmental Responsibility – Digital sustainability, renewable hosting, and efficient workflows to reduce carbon footprint.</li>
        <li>Ethical Governance – Transparency in decision-making, compliance, and fair business practices.</li>
        <li>Partnerships – Collaborating with NGOs, industry groups, and local communities to maximise impact.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Benefits of CSR Integration">
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Improved corporate reputation and brand loyalty.</li>
        <li>Increased stakeholder confidence and investor appeal.</li>
        <li>Positive social and environmental impact with measurable outcomes.</li>
        <li>Alignment with ESG and SDG initiatives for long-term sustainability.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Get Started with CSR">
      <p>We support organisations in developing actionable CSR strategies that deliver real impact for people, planet, and profit.</p>
      <p><a href="/contact" class="text-green-600 font-semibold hover:underline">Contact us</a> to begin embedding CSR into your business strategy.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>